<h1><img src="erlanim.gif">Erlang in Real Time</h1>
<p>
`Erlang in Real Time' (ISBN: 0864447434) was written by Maurice Castro
to support the course `CS584 Real Time and Concurrent Systems' at RMIT
University in 1998. A revised edition is available in postscript form
from this site in addition to the sample code used in the course.

